{"tid":2194672,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"解放軍確認尋獲五名失蹤印度青年","createTime":"2020-09-08T15:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T15:48:12.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c4ffb924fffd7674ba1566d8fc7082337952f3b8","tid":2194672,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:48:12.000Z","msg":"解放軍確認尋獲五名失蹤印度青年<br />\n<br />\n#兩岸國際 中印邊境局勢再度升級。中國軍方指摘印軍再次越過實際控制線挑釁，並鳴槍威脅；印度反指是解放軍向天鳴槍。在北京，外交部指中方已通過外交和軍事渠道，向印度提出嚴正交涉。 (9/8/23:42) 全文 (<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=404843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404843&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=400a1cf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404843&h=682f5f1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=404843</a>)"}]}